Release Information

gSyncit is a Microsoft Outlook add-in that allows
for the synchronization of Outlook calendars
contacts, notes, and tasks with your Google
account. In addition, gSyncit also supports
synchronization between Outlook and Toodledo
Pocket Informant Online, Evernote, Dropbox
Simplenote and Nozbe
